Based on android's repo script

Mirror tree
└── repo-template-mirror
    ├── git-repo.git  -- repo tool project
    ├── platform
    │   ├── manifest.git -- manifest mirror
    │   └── test.git -- project mirror
    └── repo.git  -- repo script

Projects tree
└── repo-projects
    ├── Makefile -- project file (controlled by manifest copy command)
    ├── .repo -- repo data folder
    │   ├── manifests -- manifest project
    │   ├── manifests.git
    │   ├── project-objects
    │   ├── projects
    │   └── repo -- repo tool
    └── test -- test project
        ├── .git
        └── test_folder
